<Base title="Terms of Service">
  <h1 class="page-title">Terms of Service</h1>
  <div class="about-content">
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 3, 2026</p>

    <h2>1. Acceptance of Terms</h2>
    <p>
      By accessing and using Azadi Wire ("the Service"), you agree to be bound
      by these Terms of Service. If you do not agree, do not use the Service.
    </p>

    <h2>2. Description of Service</h2>
    <p>
      Azadi Wire is a free, non-commercial news aggregator that collects and
      displays publicly available English-language news articles about Iran from
      third-party sources. We do not produce original journalism. All article
      content belongs to the respective publishers.
    </p>

    <h2>3. No Warranty</h2>
    <p>
      The Service is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind, express or
      implied. We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or timeliness of
      any information displayed. Articles are fetched automatically and
      categorized by an AI model; misclassification may occur.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Third-Party Content</h2>
    <p>
      Azadi Wire links to articles hosted by third-party news organizations. We
      are not responsible for the content, accuracy, or availability of those
      external sites. Following a link to any third-party site is at your own
